window.bookSummaryJSON = "From the creators of <i>Up and Vanished</i> and <i>To Live and Die in L.A.</i> comes an Audible Original true crime podcast set in the dark underworld of boxing. Tim ‘Doc’ Anderson was sentenced to spend the rest of his life in prison for killing his manager. So why does everyone who has known him, including his victim’s family, think he should be released? Journalist David Farrier (<i>Dark Tourist</i>, <i>Tickled</i>) explores the murky world around the boxing ring to ask: how did one of the sport’s good guys pick up a gun and fire?"; 
